purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains LOINC codes identified as survey or question panel codes, commonly used for encoding standardized assessment instruments, questionnaires, or physical assessment panels, such as Apgar scores.),(Data Element Scope: The purpose of this value set is to provide LOINC survey codes packaged as a value set for use in health IT systems and standards),(Inclusion Criteria: LOINC code of TypeName:survey and Class:PANEL.NEONAT),(Exclusion Criteria: NA)
